---
// ============================================================================
// PAGE: About / Founder ‚Äî Ali Saleh
// PURPOSE: Human introduction, grounding ArcUp in personal story and ethos
// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// NOTES:
// - Uses ArcUp scaffold v1.0 structure
// - Tone: warm, transparent, grounded
